😆 ‼️❤️ Hey everyone! Exciting news—I was just featured on the Professor Kev Show podcast! 🎙️✨ His show features the journey of young entrepreneurs. You won't want to miss it! Check it out and let me know what you think! Candace D. Washington & Maurice Andre Gillespie #professorkevshow #professorkev #kanahutchens #ctdp #connectingthedotsproject #sustainability #youngentrepreneur #leadership #environement #sustainability #sustainable #nature #conservation #circulareconomy #youths

🌻❤️ Please check out the article about our event by Block Club Chicago !! 🙏🌻 https://lnkd.in/gRzj4R7G 👈👈🏼👈🏽 It has been less than a week since the sunflower event and the seeds are already sprouting!! #nature #garden #gardening #seedlings #sunflower #summer #detox #decontamination #soil #urbanagriculture #health #environment #sustainable #sustainability #connectingthedotsproject #ctdp #kanahutchens #kavimyers #resilience #chicago #Illinois Block Club Chicago NFP

🌻🙏 Our sunflower event was a huge success! My arms and back are sore, but it was so wonderful to see everyone working together to improve the community. Our heartfelt thanks to all the volunteers and organizations for their time and resources, the master gardeners for their guidance and support, and the Westbrook family for allowing us to use the land for the project! #connectingthedotsproject #kanahutchens #ctdp #kavimyers #eastgarfieldpark #garfieldpark #chicago #sunflowers #planting #environment #community #beauty #sustainability #sustainable #sunflowercity #garfieldparkadvisorycouncil #kuumbatreahmcommunitygarden #relishchicago #breakthrough #garfieldparkcommunitycouncil #chicagotoollibrary #westbrookfamilymemorialgarden

I am thrilled to announce our new initiative, the "Sunflower Project in East Garfield Park," by Connecting The Dots Project! It will be held at 3009 W. Madison street, Chicago on June 23rd. Thank you to all the local community members and organizations for their support in making this project possible! #connectingthedotsproject #CTDP #kanahutchens #kavimyers #environment #eastgarfieldpark #Chicago #Illinois #youthinitiative #highschool #urbangreening #urbangardening #greeninitiative #urbanagriculture #sunflower #seeds #sustainability #sustainable #nature #habitat #community #communitygarden

❤️ 👍 As the co-founder of the Komically Kids Art Club at Walter Payton College Prep, I am thrilled to share some exciting news! Our club's amazing artwork, created with the incredible support of Miguel Limon, an artist and educator, will be showcased at the Design Museum Chicago! Join us on June 4th at 72 E Randolph St, Floor 1, Chicago, for an unforgettable event celebrating the creativity and talent of youths. We can't wait to see you there and share our passion for art with you‼️ #komicallykids #miguellimon #artinstituteofchicago #designmuseum #art #artists #printmaking #design #kanahutchens #walterpaytoncollegeprep #cps #chicago #illinois #youngartists #sandralao @miguellimon

‼️😱 I am shocked at how fast time flies. My junior year in high school is almost done and it has been 8 years since the screen debut of my animation!! #mrorangebabysnot #film #filmmaking #animation #kanahutchens #art #creative #highschoollife #junioryear #time

❤️✨👠 All the fellow high school students in Chicago, do you need a prom dress or suit but can't afford one? Look no further. These non-profit organizations offer free prom dresses. They have designers and great collections. Please share the info because your friend might be able to use one. And to those who live in different states, there are many similar organizations around the country. If you are interested in a similar opportunity, you should google "Prom dress giveaway near me." Good luck! 1) The Gift of Glamour: https://lnkd.in/gR3sWnxj 2) 713 Ceg & Prom Girls Rock: https://www.713ceg.org/ 3) Humble Hearts: https://lnkd.in/g8P6TvwA #ctdp #connectingthedotsproject #recycling #recycle #circularfashion #upcycling #prom #prom2024 #dresses #promdresses #chicago #illinois #giveaway #giveaways #promdressgiveaway #kanahutchens

❤️ 🙌 So thrilled to announce that my film has been invited to participate in the National Festival Tour by Asian CineVision!!!! "Asian CineVision proudly presents the National Festival Tour Featuring the year’s best independent cinema–narrative and documentary features and shorts programs, the National Festival Tour offers institutions and organizations the rare opportunity to bring new, independent Asian and Asian American films to local communities across the country." #kanahutchens #films #filmmaking #shortfilm #AAIFF #Cinevision #animation #nationalfestivaltour #AsianCineVision #art #creative #ACV
